3.10.20  1:44 am   besides the new 3d video software, what are other new struggles

     hold on just a moment, that's not a struggle

     you're facing working on some wonderful new material for the world to see?

      just the infinity disease, as normal. i might as well name the dang thing after myself, because this has been my signature move, for seemingly every moment of my entire life. it has gotten me very far, and also overwhelmed me into tiny fractalized bits, again and again; for as long as i can remember

      What if it caught on and people started using snakes to do everything, like for example, headbands or shoelaces or belts? Also, do you answer all the questions your asked on the same day that people ask them? 

     mostly

3.10.20  12:17 am   I know this is just a statement, but thank you. I've been in a huge depressive episode for some time and your songs/videos and your attitude about making art have been really inspiring lately. I feel like things are lifting and I want to get back to putting things out into the world again, and you set a really good example for someone who makes things, and makes them a certain way. You don't need to respond to this, since it's just a statement and all that, but I wanted to say thank you.

     holy barn door and entire barn structure, you've shown signs of inate friendiment

3.9.20  6:37 pm   Any tips for wanting to start composing music? (Affordable software, tips for song writing, etc)

     first just try something. try whatever is available. try the first thing that comes to mind. let me know how it went. my approach was full of failures and restlessness, but i will hesitate to give you the same advice yet, because i may have had more or different failures and restlessness than you may have. if you go out there and have some problems and let me know what the problems are, then i'm sure i will have some advice for you. i am problem champion, it's kind of my strong point
